attributes.Long form description: The student is building a shelf. They start by inspecting the base, then aligning it. Next, they assemble the legs one by one, until all four are attached to the base. Finally, they attach the top table, and tighten all the screws.

attributes.Transcription: OK. Now, please assemble this table.
